  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mm-hmm, so peaceful.",
      "zh": "嗯，真平靜。",
      "ja": "うん、とても平和だ。",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is heaven. No stress, no noise, just quiet.",
      "zh": "這裡是天堂。沒有壓力，沒有噪音，只有寧靜。",
      "ja": "ここは天国だ。ストレスもなく、騒音もなく、ただ静かだ。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Perfect, absolutely perfect, nothing can disturb this.",
      "zh": "完美，絕對完美，沒有什麼能打擾這一切。",
      "ja": "完璧だ、まったく完璧だ、何もこれを邪魔できない。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, no, no, no, stay in the dream, please!",
      "zh": "不，不，不，不，請繼續做夢！",
      "ja": "いや、いや、いや、いや、夢の中にいてください！",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, my spa, my beautiful quiet spa!",
      "zh": "不，我的水療，我美麗寧靜的水療！",
      "ja": "いや、私のスパ、私の美しい静かなスパ！",
      "time": "00:00:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Michael! Michael, you're doing it again!",
      "zh": "麥可！麥可，你又來了！",
      "ja": "マイケル！マイケル、またやってる！",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom?",
      "zh": "媽媽？",
      "ja": "ママ？",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We can't sleep, it's too loud.",
      "zh": "我們睡不著，太吵了。",
      "ja": "眠れないよ、うるさすぎる。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It sounds like a monster!",
      "zh": "聽起來像怪物！",
      "ja": "モンスターみたいな音だ！",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know, I know. Mommy will fix this.",
      "zh": "我知道，我知道。媽媽會解決的。",
      "ja": "わかってる、わかってる。ママが直すから。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No strips, these should work, I hope.",
      "zh": "沒有貼鼻貼，這些應該有效，希望如此。",
      "ja": "鼻ストリップはないけど、これでうまくいくはず、願うよ。",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just stick it on, nice and easy.",
      "zh": "就貼上去，輕鬆簡單。",
      "ja": "ただ貼るだけ、簡単だよ。",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Will it work, Mom?",
      "zh": "會有效嗎，媽媽？",
      "ja": "効くかな、ママ？",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stay still!",
      "zh": "別動！",
      "ja": "じっとしてて！",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you kidding me?",
      "zh": "你在開玩笑嗎？",
      "ja": "冗談でしょ？",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, plan B.",
      "zh": "好，方案B。",
      "ja": "よし、プランBだ。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is the chin strap for stopping snoring.",
      "zh": "這是防止打鼾的下巴帶。",
      "ja": "これはいびきを止めるためのあご紐だ。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This has to work.",
      "zh": "這一定有效。",
      "ja": "これでうまくいくはず。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That looks weird.",
      "zh": "看起來怪怪的。",
      "ja": "変な感じだね。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on, just hold still for one second.",
      "zh": "拜託，請靜止一秒。",
      "ja": "お願い、ちょっとだけじっとしてて。",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's quiet.",
      "zh": "安靜了。",
      "ja": "静かになった。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, his cheeks.",
      "zh": "等等，他的臉頰。",
      "ja": "待って、彼の頬が。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's gonna explode!",
      "zh": "他要爆炸了！",
      "ja": "彼は爆発しそうだ！",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's louder now!",
      "zh": "現在更大聲了！",
      "ja": "今はもっと大きい！",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He looks like an ninja!",
      "zh": "他看起來像忍者！",
      "ja": "彼は忍者みたいだ！",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing works, I tried everything.",
      "zh": "什麼都沒用，我試過所有方法。",
      "ja": "何も効かない、全部試したのに。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, please!",
      "zh": "媽媽，拜託！",
      "ja": "ママ、お願い！",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, that's it, he's going downstairs.",
      "zh": "好，夠了，他下樓去。",
      "ja": "よし、もういい、彼は下に行く。",
      "time": "00:02:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Michael, wake up!",
      "zh": "麥可，醒醒！",
      "ja": "マイケル、起きて！",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh?",
      "zh": "嗯？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "何？",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "zh": "怎麼了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:02:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Did I snore again?",
      "zh": "我又打鼾了嗎？",
      "ja": "またいびきをかいた？",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, and I tried the nose strips, I tried the chin strap.",
      "zh": "是的，我試了鼻貼，也試了下巴帶。",
      "ja": "そうだよ、鼻ストリップもあご紐も試した。",
      "time": "00:02:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing worked, the kids need to sleep.",
      "zh": "都沒用，孩子們需要睡覺。",
      "ja": "何も効かなかった、子供たちは寝る必要がある。",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But honey, you snore sometimes too!",
      "zh": "但是親愛的，你有時候也會打鼾！",
      "ja": "でもね、あなたも時々いびきをかくよ！",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not, Michael, go to the couch, please.",
      "zh": "我沒有，麥可，請去沙發。",
      "ja": "私はかかない、マイケル、ソファに行ってください。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "When you're really tired, you do.",
      "zh": "你真的很累的時候會的。",
      "ja": "本当に疲れている時はかくよ。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What did you say?",
      "zh": "你說什麼？",
      "ja": "何て言った？",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Nothing, I'm going!",
      "zh": "沒什麼，我走了！",
      "ja": "何でもない、行くよ！",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry, I don't mean to snore.",
      "zh": "對不起，我不是故意打鼾的。",
      "ja": "ごめん、いびきをかくつもりはなかった。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know, just go sleep on the couch, please.",
      "zh": "我知道，請去沙發睡覺。",
      "ja": "わかってる、ソファで寝てください。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The couch again, my second home.",
      "zh": "又是沙發，我的第二個家。",
      "ja": "またソファか、僕の第二の家だ。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally, peace and quiet.",
      "zh": "終於，安靜了。",
      "ja": "やっと、平和と静けさだ。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we sleep now?",
      "zh": "我們現在可以睡了嗎？",
      "ja": "もう寝ていい？",
      "time": "00:03:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, back to your room, quick.",
      "zh": "可以，快回你的房間。",
      "ja": "うん、早く自分の部屋に戻って。",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here we go again.",
      "zh": "又來了。",
      "ja": "また始まった。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Too hard, too soft, why is this couch so uncomfortable?",
      "zh": "太硬，太軟，為什麼這沙發這麼不舒服？",
      "ja": "硬すぎる、柔らかすぎる、なんでこのソファはこんなに不快なんだ？",
      "time": "00:03:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can't sleep too awake now.",
      "zh": "睡不著，現在太清醒了。",
      "ja": "眠れない、今は目が冴えてる。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I'm hungry.",
      "zh": "哦，我餓了。",
      "ja": "ああ、お腹すいた。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe just a small snack, something quick and quiet.",
      "zh": "也許吃點小點心，快速又安靜的東西。",
      "ja": "ちょっと軽く何か、早くて静かなものを。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see what do we have.",
      "zh": "看看我們有什麼。",
      "ja": "何があるか見てみよう。",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm, no, no.",
      "zh": "嗯，不，不行。",
      "ja": "うーん、ダメだ。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, spaghetti, perfect!",
      "zh": "等等，義大利麵，完美！",
      "ja": "待って、スパゲッティ、完璧！",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just boil some water, super quiet, no problem.",
      "zh": "只要煮水，超安靜，沒問題。",
      "ja": "お湯を沸かすだけ、すごく静か、問題なし。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just some water, nice and quiet, no one will know.",
      "zh": "只是水，很安靜，沒人會知道。",
      "ja": "ただの水、静かで誰も気づかない。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There we go, nice and easy.",
      "zh": "好了，很簡單。",
      "ja": "できた、簡単だ。",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Looking good, this will be delicious.",
      "zh": "看起來不錯，這會很好吃。",
      "ja": "いい感じ、美味しくなるよ。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Whoa, that's a lot of steam.",
      "zh": "哇，好多蒸氣。",
      "ja": "わあ、蒸気がすごい。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Should I turn on the fan?",
      "zh": "我該開風扇嗎？",
      "ja": "扇風機をつけるべき？",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, too loud.",
      "zh": "不，太吵了。",
      "ja": "ダメ、うるさすぎる。",
      "time": "00:04:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Everyone's sleeping, I'll just let it clear naturally.",
      "zh": "大家都在睡，我就讓它自然散去。",
      "ja": "みんな寝てるから、自然に消えるのを待とう。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Smart thinking, Michael, so smart, and it would be proud.",
      "zh": "聰明的想法，麥可，很聰明，他會驕傲的。",
      "ja": "賢い考えだ、マイケル、とても賢いよ、彼も誇りに思うだろう。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally, peace and quiet.",
      "zh": "終於，安靜了。",
      "ja": "やっと、平和と静けさだ。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The smoke alarm?",
      "zh": "煙霧警報器？",
      "ja": "煙探知機？",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no, the whole house will hear you.",
      "zh": "糟了，整個房子都會聽到。",
      "ja": "やばい、家中みんなに聞こえる。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shh, turn it off!",
      "zh": "噓，關掉它！",
      "ja": "シッ、消して！",
      "time": "00:05:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How do I turn it off?",
      "zh": "我怎麼關掉它？",
      "ja": "どうやって消すの？",
      "time": "00:05:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Chair, I need the chair, stop beeping.",
      "zh": "椅子，我需要椅子，別再響了。",
      "ja": "椅子、椅子が必要だ、鳴るのやめて。",
      "time": "00:05:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What was that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "何の音？",
      "time": "00:05:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have to get out of here.",
      "zh": "我得離開這裡。",
      "ja": "ここから出なきゃ。",
      "time": "00:05:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What was that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "何の音？",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have to get out of here.",
      "zh": "我得離開這裡。",
      "ja": "ここから出なきゃ。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Please stop, please.",
      "zh": "請停下，拜託。",
      "ja": "やめて、お願い。",
      "time": "00:06:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What, what is that noise?",
      "zh": "什麼，那是什麼聲音？",
      "ja": "何だ、その音は？",
      "time": "00:06:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is it 3 a.m.?",
      "zh": "現在是凌晨三點嗎？",
      "ja": "午前3時？",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, is there a fire?",
      "zh": "媽媽，有火災嗎？",
      "ja": "ママ、火事？",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No fire.",
      "zh": "沒有火災。",
      "ja": "火事じゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:06:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just your father, follow me.",
      "zh": "只是你爸爸，跟我來。",
      "ja": "ただお父さんだ、ついてきて。",
      "time": "00:06:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is dad in the kitchen?",
      "zh": "爸爸為什麼在廚房？",
      "ja": "なんでお父さんがキッチンにいるの？",
      "time": "00:06:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "To destroy our sleep.",
      "zh": "來破壞我們的睡眠。",
      "ja": "私たちの睡眠を壊すためだ。",
      "time": "00:06:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see what he's doing.",
      "zh": "來看看他在做什麼。",
      "ja": "彼が何をしているか見てみよう。",
      "time": "00:06:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you standing on a chair, fanning the smoke alarm with a cookbook?",
      "zh": "你站在椅子上，用食譜扇著煙霧警報器？",
      "ja": "椅子に立って、料理本で煙探知機をあおいでるの？",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was making spaghetti, and I didn't want to use the fan because it's loud.",
      "zh": "我在煮義大利麵，不想開風扇因為太吵。",
      "ja": "スパゲッティを作ってて、扇風機はうるさいから使いたくなかった。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But then the smoke alarm, and I thought if I just...",
      "zh": "但接著煙霧警報響了，我想如果我只是…",
      "ja": "でも煙探知機が鳴って、もしこれを…",
      "time": "00:07:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Turn on the fan now!",
      "zh": "現在開風扇吧！",
      "ja": "今すぐ扇風機をつけて！",
      "time": "00:07:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So I was worried the fan would be too loud.",
      "zh": "所以我擔心風扇會太吵。",
      "ja": "だから扇風機がうるさすぎるのを心配してた。",
      "time": "00:07:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And instead, I set off every smoke alarm in the house.",
      "zh": "結果，我觸發了整個房子的煙霧警報。",
      "ja": "その代わりに、家中の煙探知機を全部鳴らしちゃった。",
      "time": "00:07:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A smoke alarm, at 3 a.m. for pasta, because you didn't want to be loud.",
      "zh": "凌晨三點因為義大利麵而響起的煙霧警報，因為你不想吵。",
      "ja": "午前3時にパスタのために鳴った煙探知機、うるさくしたくなかったから。",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was trying to be considerate, and I'm really hungry.",
      "zh": "我只是想體貼大家，而且我真的很餓。",
      "ja": "気を使おうとしただけで、本当にお腹が空いてたんだ。",
      "time": "00:07:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you serious?",
      "zh": "你認真的嗎？",
      "ja": "マジで？",
      "time": "00:07:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just finish your pasta.",
      "zh": "快吃完你的義大利麵吧。",
      "ja": "パスタを食べ終わって。",
      "time": "00:07:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're all awake now anyway.",
      "zh": "反正我們現在都醒了。",
      "ja": "もうみんな起きてるし。",
      "time": "00:07:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, crisis sort of over.",
      "zh": "好吧，危機算是過去了。",
      "ja": "よし、危機は一応終わった。",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is really good!",
      "zh": "這真的很好吃！",
      "ja": "これ、本当に美味しい！",
      "time": "00:08:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wonderful.",
      "zh": "太棒了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:08:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm so happy for you.",
      "zh": "我真為你高興。",
      "ja": "君のために嬉しいよ。",
      "time": "00:08:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, much better.",
      "zh": "啊，好多了。",
      "ja": "ああ、ずっといい。",
      "time": "00:08:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm full now.",
      "zh": "我現在飽了。",
      "ja": "もうお腹いっぱい。",
      "time": "00:08:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, now I can sleep.",
      "zh": "好了，現在我可以睡了。",
      "ja": "よし、これで寝られる。",
      "time": "00:08:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night, everyone!",
      "zh": "晚安，大家！",
      "ja": "おやすみ、みんな！",
      "time": "00:08:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And he's snoring again.",
      "zh": "他又開始打鼾了。",
      "ja": "そして彼はいびきをかいている。",
      "time": "00:08:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not this time.",
      "zh": "這次沒有。",
      "ja": "今回は違う。",
      "time": "00:08:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's on his back.",
      "zh": "他仰躺著。",
      "ja": "彼は仰向けだ。",
      "time": "00:08:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's why he snores.",
      "zh": "這就是他打鼾的原因。",
      "ja": "それが彼がいびきをかく理由だ。",
      "time": "00:08:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We need to turn him on his side.",
      "zh": "我們得讓他側睡。",
      "ja": "彼を横向きにしなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:08:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Emma, you push from that side.",
      "zh": "艾瑪，你從那邊推。",
      "ja": "エマ、そっちから押して。",
      "time": "00:09:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack, help me from this side.",
      "zh": "傑克，你從這邊幫我。",
      "ja": "ジャック、こっちから手伝って。",
      "time": "00:09:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Got it.",
      "zh": "知道了。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:09:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He looks really heavy.",
      "zh": "他看起來很重。",
      "ja": "彼は本当に重そうだ。",
      "time": "00:09:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's why we all push together.",
      "zh": "所以我們一起推。",
      "ja": "だからみんなで一緒に押すんだ。",
      "time": "00:09:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "On 3, 1, 2, 3, push.",
      "zh": "三秒倒數，1、2、3，推。",
      "ja": "3で、1、2、3、押して。",
      "time": "00:09:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think it worked!",
      "zh": "我覺得成功了！",
      "ja": "うまくいったと思う！",
      "time": "00:09:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shh, don't jinx it.",
      "zh": "噓，別說壞話。",
      "ja": "シッ、ジンクスはやめて。",
      "time": "00:09:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now we wedge him in place so he can't roll back.",
      "zh": "現在我們把他固定住，讓他不能翻回去。",
      "ja": "今彼を挟んで、戻れないようにする。",
      "time": "00:09:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like a pillow sandwich.",
      "zh": "像枕頭三明治一樣。",
      "ja": "枕のサンドイッチみたいに。",
      "time": "00:09:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "zh": "沒錯。",
      "ja": "その通り。",
      "time": "00:09:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He can't roll over now.",
      "zh": "他現在翻不了身了。",
      "ja": "彼はもう寝返りできない。",
      "time": "00:09:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mission accomplished.",
      "zh": "任務完成。",
      "ja": "ミッション完了。",
      "time": "00:09:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's get some sleep.",
      "zh": "我們去睡覺吧。",
      "ja": "寝よう。",
      "time": "00:09:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally, it's so quiet.",
      "zh": "終於，好安靜。",
      "ja": "やっと、とても静かだ。",
      "time": "00:09:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bow before anything else happens.",
      "zh": "在發生其他事之前先鞠躬。",
      "ja": "他に何か起こる前にお辞儀しよう。",
      "time": "00:09:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night, Mom.",
      "zh": "晚安，媽媽。",
      "ja": "おやすみ、ママ。",
      "time": "00:09:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night for real this time.",
      "zh": "這次是真的晚安了。",
      "ja": "今度こそ本当におやすみ。",
      "time": "00:09:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally, peace, quiet sleep.",
      "zh": "終於，平靜安眠。",
      "ja": "やっと、平和で静かな眠り。",
      "time": "00:09:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's so quiet.",
      "zh": "好安靜。",
      "ja": "とても静かだ。",
      "time": "00:10:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Too quiet.",
      "zh": "太安靜了。",
      "ja": "静かすぎる。",
      "time": "00:10:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What was that?",
      "zh": "那是什麼？",
      "ja": "何の音？",
      "time": "00:10:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad, are you there?",
      "zh": "爸爸，你在嗎？",
      "ja": "パパ、いる？",
      "time": "00:10:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you eating cookies without me?",
      "zh": "你在沒我的情況下吃餅乾嗎？",
      "ja": "僕抜きでクッキー食べてる？",
      "time": "00:10:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm scared.",
      "zh": "我害怕。",
      "ja": "怖いよ。",
      "time": "00:10:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I need to find my sister.",
      "zh": "我得找我妹妹。",
      "ja": "妹を探さなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:10:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello?",
      "zh": "哈囉？",
      "ja": "もしもし？",
      "time": "00:10:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you awake?",
      "zh": "你醒著嗎？",
      "ja": "起きてる？",
      "time": "00:10:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Emma, you awake?",
      "zh": "艾瑪，你醒了嗎？",
      "ja": "エマ、起きてる？",
      "time": "00:10:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:10:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can't sleep.",
      "zh": "睡不著。",
      "ja": "眠れない。",
      "time": "00:10:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's too quiet.",
      "zh": "太安靜了。",
      "ja": "静かすぎる。",
      "time": "00:10:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't like it.",
      "zh": "我不喜歡這樣。",
      "ja": "嫌だ。",
      "time": "00:10:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It feels weird.",
      "zh": "感覺怪怪的。",
      "ja": "変な感じがする。",
      "time": "00:10:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Me neither.",
      "zh": "我也是。",
      "ja": "僕もだ。",
      "time": "00:10:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Like something's wrong.",
      "zh": "好像有什麼不對勁。",
      "ja": "何かがおかしいみたい。",
      "time": "00:10:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's too quiet without Dad.",
      "zh": "沒有爸爸太安靜了。",
      "ja": "パパがいないと静かすぎる。",
      "time": "00:10:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是啊。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:10:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I missed the noise.",
      "zh": "我想念那些聲音。",
      "ja": "あの音が恋しい。",
      "time": "00:10:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What if monsters come?",
      "zh": "如果怪物來怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "もしモンスターが来たら？",
      "time": "00:10:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Dad will scare them away.",
      "zh": "爸爸會嚇跑他們。",
      "ja": "パパが追い払ってくれる。",
      "time": "00:10:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Even in his sleep.",
      "zh": "即使在睡覺時。",
      "ja": "寝ている間でも。",
      "time": "00:10:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we sleep with Dad on the couch?",
      "zh": "我們可以和爸爸一起睡沙發嗎？",
      "ja": "パパと一緒にソファで寝てもいい？",
      "time": "00:10:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:10:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The couch is safe.",
      "zh": "沙發很安全。",
      "ja": "ソファは安全だよ。",
      "time": "00:11:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go downstairs.",
      "zh": "我們下樓去吧。",
      "ja": "下に行こう。",
      "time": "00:11:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just want to hear Dad's snoring.",
      "zh": "我只想聽爸爸打鼾。",
      "ja": "パパのいびきを聞きたいだけ。",
      "time": "00:11:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is that weird?",
      "zh": "這很奇怪嗎？",
      "ja": "変かな？",
      "time": "00:11:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's not weird.",
      "zh": "不奇怪。",
      "ja": "変じゃないよ。",
      "time": "00:11:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I know what you mean.",
      "zh": "我懂你的意思。",
      "ja": "君の気持ちわかるよ。",
      "time": "00:11:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It sounds silly, but Dad's snoring makes me feel safe.",
      "zh": "聽起來傻，但爸爸的鼾聲讓我感到安全。",
      "ja": "馬鹿みたいだけど、パパのいびきは安心する。",
      "time": "00:11:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Finally.",
      "zh": "終於。",
      "ja": "やっと。",
      "time": "00:11:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Listen, the snoring beast is here.",
      "zh": "聽，打鼾怪獸來了。",
      "ja": "聞いて、いびきの怪物が来た。",
      "time": "00:11:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's still snoring.",
      "zh": "他還在打鼾。",
      "ja": "まだいびきをかいてる。",
      "time": "00:11:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good, it's good.",
      "zh": "好，這很好。",
      "ja": "いいね、いいよ。",
      "time": "00:11:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's good.",
      "zh": "那很好。",
      "ja": "それはいい。",
      "time": "00:11:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Right here.",
      "zh": "就在這裡。",
      "ja": "ここだよ。",
      "time": "00:11:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Bye, Dad.",
      "zh": "再見，爸爸。",
      "ja": "バイバイ、パパ。",
      "time": "00:11:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Close enough to hear him.",
      "zh": "夠近能聽到他。",
      "ja": "聞こえるくらい近い。",
      "time": "00:11:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Better now?",
      "zh": "現在好點了嗎？",
      "ja": "今は良くなった？",
      "time": "00:11:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:11:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Much better.",
      "zh": "好多了。",
      "ja": "ずっといい。",
      "time": "00:11:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can sleep now.",
      "zh": "我現在可以睡了。",
      "ja": "もう寝られる。",
      "time": "00:11:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good night, snoring monster.",
      "zh": "晚安，打鼾怪獸。",
      "ja": "おやすみ、いびきの怪物。",
      "time": "00:11:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:11:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Make it stop.",
      "zh": "讓它停下來。",
      "ja": "やめてほしい。",
      "time": "00:12:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why did I set an alarm?",
      "zh": "我為什麼要設鬧鐘？",
      "ja": "なんでアラームをセットしたんだ？",
      "time": "00:12:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's Saturday.",
      "zh": "今天是星期六。",
      "ja": "今日は土曜日だ。",
      "time": "00:12:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, I'm up shopping.",
      "zh": "好，我起床去買東西。",
      "ja": "よし、起きて買い物に行く。",
      "time": "00:12:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Morning already.",
      "zh": "已經早上了。",
      "ja": "もう朝だ。",
      "time": "00:12:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow, I slept well.",
      "zh": "哇，我睡得很好。",
      "ja": "わあ、よく眠れた。",
      "time": "00:12:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You little sneaks came down here.",
      "zh": "你們這些小搗蛋下來了。",
      "ja": "こっそりここに来たな。",
      "time": "00:12:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You needed your old dad snoring after all.",
      "zh": "畢竟你們還是需要老爸的鼾聲。",
      "ja": "結局はお父さんのいびきが必要だったんだな。",
      "time": "00:12:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And it should be down by now.",
      "zh": "現在應該已經消了。",
      "ja": "もう消えてるはずだ。",
      "time": "00:12:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We have shopping at 8.30.",
      "zh": "我們8點半要去買東西。",
      "ja": "8時半に買い物がある。",
      "time": "00:12:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna, honey, you awake.",
      "zh": "安娜，親愛的，你醒了嗎？",
      "ja": "アンナ、ハニー、起きてる？",
      "time": "00:12:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We're going to be late.",
      "zh": "我們要遲到了。",
      "ja": "遅刻するよ。",
      "time": "00:12:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Anna, I'm coming in.",
      "zh": "安娜，我進來了。",
      "ja": "アンナ、入るよ。",
      "time": "00:13:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, my God.",
      "zh": "天啊。",
      "ja": "ああ、神様。",
      "time": "00:13:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She is snoring.",
      "zh": "她在打鼾。",
      "ja": "彼女がいびきをかいてる。",
      "time": "00:13:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So she snores too, even louder than me, ironic.",
      "zh": "所以她也打鼾，還比我大聲，真諷刺。",
      "ja": "だから彼女もいびきをかく、僕より大きいなんて皮肉だ。",
      "time": "00:13:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Poor thing, she was so tired.",
      "zh": "可憐，她真的很累。",
      "ja": "かわいそうに、彼女はとても疲れてた。",
      "time": "00:13:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No wonder she's snoring.",
      "zh": "難怪她會打鼾。",
      "ja": "いびきをかくのも無理ない。",
      "time": "00:13:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "She earned this sleep.",
      "zh": "她值得這場睡眠。",
      "ja": "彼女はこの眠りに値する。",
      "time": "00:13:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sleep well, honey.",
      "zh": "好好睡吧，親愛的。",
      "ja": "ゆっくり寝てね、ハニー。",
      "time": "00:13:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Shopping can wait.",
